title: Steve Dinan
description:
Steve Dinan has been a master behind building racing engines and teams but he got his street cred modifying BMWs. His cars have always been fast, reliable, and modified in a comprehensive method. His new company is called Carbahn Autoworks.

This podcast is available as a video! https://youtu.be/EoRTlS19w6k

Check out Steve's Carbahn Autoworks here: https://carbahnautoworks.com/racing-products-service/

Follow us!

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman @carbahn_autoworks
